data.description: A spacious and impeccably maintained home backing to a tranquil canal in central Meridian! This beautifully updated residence radiates traditional elegance, featuring an immaculate interior with open-concept living, a completely renovated kitchen (2022), a main-level primary wing, and a fabulous upstairs bonus room. Stretching over ~3500 square feet, the floorplan provides generous living quarters for entertaining on a grand or intimate scale, and an abundance of private spaces to retreat to. The stunning kitchen remodel was designed for the at-home chef, including an oversized prep island lined with generous seating, sparkling quartz countertops, and a stainless-steel appliance package featuring dual ovens and dishwashers, and a gas cooktop. Tall ceilings and custom finishes extend into the primary wing, complete with a cozy gas fireplace and luxurious en suite bathroom equipped with dual vanities, an indulgent soaker tub, a walk-in shower, and a large walk-in closet.
